  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "OUTLET SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Ensure all activities within the department is in proper.</li><li>Co-ordinated and team members are briefed daily during each shift.</li><li>Ensure the daily operations are run in an order and proper manner.</li><li>Provide guidance and training to junior staff to achieve guest's satisfication.</li><li>Assist in achieving the revenue target by upselling and recommending menu items to guests.</li><li>Assist and recommend ways to reduce wastage and efficient use of resources.</li><li>Ensure guests are properly served and ensure that staff express courtesy, efficiency in dealing with guests.</li><li>Ensure a harmonious working relationship between colleagues with proper and fair distribution of work load.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Experience in F&B will be an added advantage</li><li>Team player with adequate effective communication skills</li><li>Punctual and good working attitude</li><li>Provide excellent customer service</li><li>Training will be provided</li><li>Able to work weekends & public holidays</li><li>Able to start work immediately or at short notice</li><li>Handling of Non-Halal ingredients as our restaurant is not Halal certified</li><li>Good customer service and interpersonal skills</li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 5,
